{"tid":803218,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"贏國報紙：長期不看電視和新聞聯播，容易患上憂鬱症及有自殺念頭","createTime":"2018-09-02T05:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T07:05:55.000Z","uid":136994,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"18236c04482431309e7d15e0778a9f4fa7167cca","tid":803218,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:51:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180902/58635500\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180902%2F58635500&d=nP0iKoujsGWWgNThry21MKMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=33b5eeaa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180902%2F58635500&h=a04f3cf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180902/58635500</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180902/large/1535862112_dbc5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180902%2Flarge%2F1535862112_dbc5.jpg&h=9acaca8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地的官媒不時都出現相當駭人聽聞的新聞，近日一份地方報大字標題報道一項「最新研究」，稱「長期不看電視和新聞聯播，容易患上憂鬱症」，引發不少網民質疑，要是這樣神奇，「新聞聯播也可以入精神科專用藥典」，有網民更稱，數十年來不看新聞聯播，還是好好的，亦有網民質疑官媒這樣報道，「越來越多的人可以被送進精神病院了」。<br />\n<br />\n網上廣傳的照片，指這是一份名為「鶴壁廣電傳媒」的報道，引述「最近一所國家重點大學科研室經過三年臨床研究與觀察」，稱觀察3,000名自願者，證明不喜歡看電視和新聞聯播的人，「非常容易產生焦慮和孤獨感，而且容易對社會和國家產生不信任感和懷疑的態度，時間一長，輕者會得憂鬱症，重者會產生自殺的念頭」。<br />\n<br />\n更神奇的，是報道指讓憂鬱症病人「適當的看些電視和新聞聯播」，以「一周為一個療程，三個療程內就能緩解情的壓力，病情有好轉的跡象」。<br />\n<br />\n這篇文章在網上廣傳，引發網民議論紛紛：<br />\n<br />\nA見設計：讓我憂鬱死吧！<br />\n<br />\n樓中吹笛：天天看新聞聯播會得甚麼病呢？<br />\n<br />\n浪哥映客浪三浪JCZ：新聞聯播應該收掛號費&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nqjzhch：看來《新聞聯播》也可以入精神科專用藥典！<br />\n<br />\n迷踪派行者：有心理疾病的，看不看新聞聯播一樣都會犯病。<br />\n<br />\n藏南達旺_14424：政府某些領導抑鬱自殺的不在少數，難道他們不看新聞聯播？"},{"pid":"80789c81fcaac6ed98ee2f493de311ee47d18e76","tid":803218,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:52:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dbc507681bd61ddbfbc0031387d8cdbf04c11de","tid":803218,"uid":132587,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:53:47.000Z","msg":"但係睇左智力會不斷倒退 你會揀邊樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0cf10517fcffdb993368f164445d0ae5185cab","tid":803218,"uid":94828,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:54:54.000Z","msg":"長期唔睇人吹奏中国<br />\n真係會因為自己係中国人而想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"addc862937db3f0931a63be1153d9a599e8feaa5","tid":803218,"uid":9104,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:58:21.000Z","msg":"諗起black mirror  fifteen million merits <br />\n唔想睇要俾錢 冇錢俾就一定要睇 合埋眼都唔得"},{"pid":"17d1d753469aeff35de9dd6c027ebf47699726e2","tid":803218,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:59:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7616780a316c8b6f32ccfe62b215351194f7207","tid":803218,"uid":31186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T06:55:48.000Z","msg":"咁係唔係全世界人都好易有精神病<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a319c959141096017cf67955df416db48eeae0","tid":803218,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:04:20.000Z","msg":"所以要睇新聞<br />\n睇下支那人又派咩膠<br />\n有咩新嘅死法<br />\n愉悅解壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b59a1f780f394ec94d24a2c3bc2f808427fd7a93","tid":803218,"uid":85168,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:05:55.000Z","msg":"知道社會現實，又唔能返轉頭，扮瞓著，洗唔到自己腦，係幾抑鬱嘅"}]}